description:
In the upcoming 2026 Ruffles NBA All-Star Celebrity Game on February 13, 2026, 7:00 PM ET: if the team coached by Giannis Antetokounmpo wins, the market will resolve to "Antetokounmpo". If the team coached by Anthony Anderson wins, the market will resolve to "Anderson". 

If the 2026 Ruffles NBA All-Star Celebrity Game ends in a tie, this market will resolve to 50-50.

If the game is cancelled, postponed beyond March 1, 2026, at 11:59 PM ET, or there is otherwise no winner declared within that timeframe, this market will resolve to 50-50.

The resolution source for this market will be official information from the National Basketball Association (NBA); however, a consensus of credible reporting may also be used.
